# Google Cloud Vision API (for receipt OCR) - set one of:
# 1. GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/service-account-key.json (local)
# 2. GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON={"type":"service_account",...} (e.g. Vercel: paste full JSON as one line)
# 3. Or run: gcloud auth application-default login (local)
